org.framed.orm.model

Interface Relationship

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Relation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RelationshipImpl

    public interface Relationship
extends Relation
    A representation of the model object 'Relationship'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Second Parthood
    • Second Lower
    • First Lower
    • First Upper
    • Second Upper
    • First Parthood
    • Rlship Constraints
    • Source Label
    • Target Label
    • First Lower Upper
    • Second Lower Upper

    See Also:
    OrmPackage.getRelationship()

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<RelationshipConstraint> getRlshipConstraints()
